Class DownloadQueueClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • DownloadQueueClient

  • public class DownloadQueueClient
extends java.lang.Object
    This class interacts with the download queue web service. For this communication to work, java classes will have to be generated from the "DownloadQueueExternalBasic.wsdl". The classes are automatically generated when executing the "mvn clean package" command. The cxf-plugin with goal: wsdl2java handles this. As the classes are auto-generated, they are put in the "target/generated-sources/cxf" directory.
